# Percentage

## Topics Covered
- Basic percentage concepts
- Increase and decrease
- Conversion (fraction to percentage)

## Key Formulas

Percentage = (Value / Total) × 100

Increase % = (Increase / Original Value) × 100

Decrease % = (Decrease / Original Value) × 100

## Practice Done
Solved aptitude problems based on percentages.

## Conclusion
Improved speed and accuracy in solving percentage problems.
